A cozy, warmly-lit artist's studio in the style of Studio Ghibli, where a friendly round robot with gentle glowing eyes sits at a wooden drafting table, using delicate mechanical arms to paint on a canvas. The canvas displays a whimsical landscape coming to life, with tiny painted birds appearing to flutter off the surface. Scattered around the cluttered but charming workspace are jars of colorful pigments, worn brushes, and stacks of illustrated papers. Soft afternoon sunlight streams through a large arched window covered in climbing ivy, casting dappled shadows across the wooden floorboards. A small cat spirit curls up sleeping among the art supplies. The atmosphere is magical yet productive, blending technology and traditional artistry in harmonious collaboration.
